column1: Earnings are paid out on the 15th of every month by 11:59 PM (EST) for all sales made during the previous calendar month. If you have not received your payment by the 16th of the month, notify us at community@teepublic.com (please do not email us regarding missing payment before the 16th). Live in a different time zone?
